## Limitations
The findings are based on available articles and reports, which may not cover all aspects of business adaptations during the pandemic. The focus was primarily on insights from Forbes, which may not represent the full spectrum of strategies employed by businesses globally. Additionally, the rapidly changing nature of the pandemic means that new strategies and adaptations may have emerged since the publication of the sources used.